---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="VoIP Phone Systems for Businesses in Hamilton & Waikato"
  description="Central Communications supply, install & service VoIP phone systems with Yeastar, Fanvil, Asterisk & Yealink. Cloud and onsite PBX for businesses in Hamilton and the Waikato."
>
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-tag">Services — VoIP</span>
      <h1 class="page-title">Voice over IP<br /><em>Phone Systems</em></h1>
      <p class="page-sub">Cloud & onsite PBX solutions that unify your team, wherever they are.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">
        <div class="prose">
          <h2>VoIP with Onsite &amp; Cloud Based PBX Options</h2>
          <p>
            Central Communications supply, install &amp; service only the highest quality phones and phone
            systems. With Yeastar, Fanvil, Asterisk &amp; Mikrotik, all bases are covered. If you want
            cutting-edge phone software then Central Communications can point you in the right direction
            with feature-rich, user-friendly systems.
          </p>
          <p>
            We can unify your cell phones, at-home remote workers, all your remote offices, and call centres.
            Whether you need a simple desk phone or a complete enterprise communications platform, we'll use
            the best technology for your business.
          </p>

          <h2>Our VoIP Brands</h2>
          <div class="brands-grid">
            <img src="/assets/images/yeastar.svg" alt="Yeastar" width="120" height="40" />
            <img src="/assets/images/fanvil.svg" alt="Fanvil" width="120" height="40" />
            <img src="/assets/images/asterisk.svg" alt="Asterisk" width="120" height="40" />
            <img src="/assets/images/yealink.svg" alt="Yealink" width="120" height="40" />
          </div>

          <h2>What's included?</h2>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>Onsite PBX hardware supply and installation</li>
            <li>Cloud-based hosted PBX options</li>
            <li>Mobile &amp; desktop softphone integration</li>
            <li>Voicemail, auto-attendant &amp; call queues</li>
            <li>Remote worker &amp; multi-site connectivity</li>
            <li>Ongoing support &amp; maintenance</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar">
          <div class="cta-box">
            <h3>Ready to upgrade your phones?</h3>
            <p>Call us or send a message and we'll get in touch to discuss the right solution for your business.</p>
            <a href="tel:+6480084800038" class="btn btn-ember">0800 848 0038</a>
            <a href="/#contact" class="btn btn-outline" style="margin-top:0.75rem;">Send a message</a>
          </div>
          <img src="/assets/images/posts/voip-graphic.jpg" alt="VoIP phone systems" class="sidebar-img" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    color: #e8f1ff;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem;
  }
  .page-title em { font-style: normal; color: #0ea5e9; }
  .page-sub { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #7ea3c8; max-width: 520px; }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 340px;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .brands-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }
  .brands-grid img {
    height: 32px;
    width: auto;
    filter: brightness(0) invert(0.6);
    transition: filter 0.2s;
  }
  .brands-grid img:hover { filter: none; }

  .feature-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.6rem;
  }
  .feature-list li {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    color: #1e3a5f;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .feature-list li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.6rem;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: #0ea5e9;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .sidebar { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; position: sticky; top: 6rem; }

  .cta-box {
    background: #0c1d35;
    border: 1px solid rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.15);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 1.75rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  .cta-box h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #e8f1ff; margin: 0; }
  .cta-box p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: #7ea3c8; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6; }
  .cta-box .btn-outline { color: #e8f1ff; border-color: rgba(232, 241, 255, 0.35); }
  .cta-box .btn-outline:hover { color: #38bdf8; border-color: #38bdf8; }

  .sidebar-img {
    border-radius: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.12);
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .content-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .sidebar { position: static; }
  }
</style>
